OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA very warm
OL,6,Fevening and staying sunny for most.
OL,7,FIsolated thunderstorms are possible,
OL,8,Fmost likely in eastern counties,
OL,9,Fpotentially bringing large hail and
OL,10,Ffrequent lightning but most places
OL,11,Fwill stay dry. Remaining rather warm
OL,12,Fovernight with often clear skies.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FAnother largely sunny and
OL,15,Fhot day, but possibly turning murky in
OL,16,Fthe Isles of Scilly, with low cloud
OL,17,Freaching west Cornwall by the evening.
OL,18,FFreshening easterly winds, gusty in
OL,19,Fplaces.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
